// swag global type overrides — see https://github.com/swaggo/swag#use-with-golang-internal-package
//
// Kubernetes' resource.Quantity is *string-shaped at the wire level* (e.g. "1", "2Gi"),
// but its Go struct exposes a `Format` enum field that swag introspects, producing an
// unusable nested object in the generated SDKs. Treat it as a plain string everywhere.
replace k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/resource.Quantity string
